node.text: Gold confetti falling from the ceiling is very familiar to me…… 💜💛💜💛💜💛Mamba Forever.

I was reluctant to get away but I’m so glad I did it! It was so nice to enjoy life a little bit and not think about everything I have on my plate. This was so good for my soul. Thank you so much for an amazing weekend Domenico & Stefano @dolcegabbana ❤️🇮🇹
